  <Target Name="_GenerateRestoreProjectPathItems" DependsOnTargets="_GenerateRestoreProjectPathItemsAllFrameworks;_GenerateRestoreProjectPathItemsCurrentProject" Returns="@(_CurrentRestoreProjectPathItems)">
